Original clock publications
---------------------------
- GrimAge (V1): Lu AT, et al. "DNA methylation GrimAge strongly predicts
  lifespan and healthspan." Aging (Albany NY), 2019. PMC6366976.
- GrimAge V2: Lu AT, et al. Aging (Albany NY), 2022. PMC9792204.
- Horvath multi-tissue clock: Horvath S. Genome Biology, 2013. (DOI
  10.1186/gb-2013-14-10-r115)
- Hannum clock: Hannum G, et al. Molecular Cell, 2013.
- PhenoAge (Levine): Levine ME, et al. Aging (Albany NY), 2018. Article 101414.

